metadata.name: MWWM
metadata.description:
MWMWMW

A mesmerizing wave, the first pangs which hit your drums tip and tap softly.  Fingers dance across a keyboard... A... C... D... E... The sounds melt.

The taps on your dreams reach deep.  The tips of your rems drone hard.  Look.  The light within the light reveals nothing.  So now, eyes closed, look.

WMWMWM

A weswerizng mave, unseen but not unheard.  

*Andrew Shuan Dang*
*2022*

*"What a way to kick off the year, in the cozy corners of home, a bit of isolation for safety from the spreading virus, but with my family and with my cat.  She napped through half of my painting time sleeping on the red blanket.  This is my first NFT.  Please look on!"*
